text: Cornel Oțelea (19 November 1940 – 22 January 2025) was a Romanian handball player. He won the World Championships three times. Oțelea died on 22 January 2025, at the age of 84. ==References== Category:1940 births Category:2025 deaths Category:Romanian sportspeople Category:Handball players
title: Cornel Oțelea
